      "writtenOn": "2026-06-11T17:28:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m open to changing this, but this seems like the simple solution for a single markdown file. A solution that involves creating and pushing commits back to the repo is definitely more complicated.\n\nAlso, unless I\u0027m really misreading the jjb yamls for most other jobs in gerrit-ci-scripts, they\u0027re already using [`publishers.archive`](https://jenkins-job-builder.readthedocs.io/en/latest/publishers.html#publishers.archive), correct? So, why not continue that here?",
      "parentUuid": "8266b128_3d12d1d1",
      "revId": "b3591506acd8e5a8dfba499e99a1ac91a1f81546",
      "serverId": "173816e5-2b9a-37c3-8a2e-48639d4f1153"
